      </infoLinks>
      <profiles>
        <profile name="Spirit of the Martyr" typeId="0fe1-877f-d5ab-dcc5" typeName="Act of Faith" hidden="false" id="47f0-e19c-6509-e1b3">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Ability" typeId="8973-fda0-fb3b-ebce">This Act of Faith is used in the Assault phase. If successful, do not remove any models in the unit if they are killed before they have attacked. Instead, place them on their side. After all other models involved in the assault have made their attacks, any mortally injured model placed on its side gets to make a single attack. After these attacks have been made, any models on their side are removed as casualties.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
          <attributes>
            <attribute name="Ability" typeId="e6f8-e3ed-4aba-5db7">This Act of Faith is used in the Assault phase. If successful, do not remove any models in the unit if they are killed before they have attacked. Instead, place them on their side. After all other models involved in the assault have made their attacks, any mortally injured model placed on its side gets to make a single attack. After these attacks have been made, any models on their side are removed as casualties.</attribute>
          </attributes>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
